title: Master Lock Receiver Lock, 1/2 in. and 5/8 in. Swivel Head Receiver Locks, Weather Resistant Automotive Receiver Lock with Keys
description: The Master Lock 2866DAT features 1/2in (13mm) and 5/8in (16mm) Swivel Head receiver locks. The receiver lock includes the Push to Lock locking mechanism, easily used by pushing the lock body firmly onto the pin and removing the key. The Weather Tough seal and water tight cap provides additional protection from moisture and dirt. 4-pin cylinder for added pick resistance
